{"type":null,"faqId":37058,"title":"白色表带脏了如何清洁？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>当您的表带脏了的时候，建议您可以使用沾水的纸巾或湿布擦拭、清洁表带，在清洁的时候请注意：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1、请勿使用烈性化学制品、清洗剂或强洗涤剂清洁设备或其配件，避免对表带或耳机造成腐蚀和损伤；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、清洁和维护前，请注意将手环关机并断开与其他设备的所有连接或线缆；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3、手环具有IP57及防尘防水，能够满足大家的日常使用，但是依然有可能避免不了水汽侵袭，所以清洁后请使用干布或干纸巾彻底擦干并放置足够长的时间，以避免残余水汽在内部凝结，造成机体伤害</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2222","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750140000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":56,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为手环,B2,表带清洁,腕带清洁","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}